### Payment Processing API Examples
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@paymentIntentId = pi_xxx

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Create Payment Intent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/intent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Payment for order #123",
  "metadata": {
    "orderId": "123",
    "userId": "456"
  }
}

### Get Payment Intent
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/intent/{{paymentIntentId}}

### Confirm Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentIntentId": "{{paymentIntentId}}"
}

### Create Full Refund
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/refund
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentIntentId": "{{paymentIntentId}}"
}

### Create Partial Refund
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/refund
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentIntentId": "{{paymentIntentId}}",
  "amount": 50.00
}

### List Payment Intents
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/intents?limit=10

### List Payment Intents with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/intents?limit=10&starting_after=pi_xxx
